title: Friday Post Show (10-15-21)
itunes:title: Friday Post Show (10-15-21)
description:
Bobby starts by sharing answers to questions from the BTEAM Facebook page. There are all questions listeners would ask him if he was on truth serum. We talk about the TV show moment that recently made Bobby cry. We also get into a discussion about new TV shows, Banksy and celebrities. Eddie shares that he is done with road rage.
